  "text": "RNA was prepared from three controls, two LPB 5.4, two LPB 7.4 and two LPB 7.9 preparations, using Trizol reagent (Invitrogen, Pacely, Scotland) followed by purification on conditions were according to the manufacturer's instructions. Glyceraldehyde 3-phosphate dehydrogenase was amplified as an internal standard. Data were calculated using the comparative Ct method which presents the data as a fold-difference in expression levels relative to a calibrator sample [CITATION_1] .",
